data.title: UEFA Champions League 2010/11
data.meta_description: Jack Wilshere - UEFA Champions League 2010/11, Arsenal FC
data.text:
The pictures show Jack Wilshere during the 6:0 win against Braga in the Champions League Group H match on 15th September 2010.

Group H
